A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: 3/10 The prequel trilogy had rough effects\, poor acting and cliche dialogue\, yet the seeds of an epic story. This was the inverse. Visuals were amazing\, acting was on point\, but the story bends over backwards for political messaging and often times does make sense of or explain what is happening. Characters look the part on the outside\, yet I couldn't care less what becomes of them or this trilogy.
